I"æ<p>CATHAI (cluster analysis tool for healthcare-associated infections) is an interactive web-based visualization platform that couples WGS informed clustering with associated metadata, thereby converting sequencing data into informative and accessible clinical information for the management of healthcare-associated infections (HAI) and nosocomial outbreaks.</p>

<!--more-->

<p>All code associated with this application are free available from <a href="https://github.com/FordeGenomics/cathai">CATHAIâ€™s github</a>. A demonstration version of CATHAI is available online at <a href="https://cathai.fordelab.com">cathai.fordelab.com</a>.</p>

